{"type": "article", "id": 12793, "title": "王大仁没有续约，确定离开巴黎世家", "description": "明年巴黎时装周还能看一回他给这品牌的设计", "date": "2015-07-29T21:51:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 1548, "name": "开云集团"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112945x2r4vemtgwXkzEQn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/alexander-wang-balenciaga-10194011/\" target=\"_blank\">据 <span>WWD </span>报道</a>，<span>Alexander Wang</span>（王大仁）将不再与开云集团续约，卸任其旗下巴黎世家（<span>Balenciaga</span>）创意总监这一职位。（而本月初我们曾报道过王大仁可能离开巴黎世家的消息，分析了<span>巴黎世家与王大仁的状况，</span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/11707.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看</a>。）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112944GzN1KZ06LtYBvIF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t所以 <span>2016 </span>年的巴黎时装周上你看到的巴黎世家将会是 <span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/2169\" target=\"_blank\">Alexander Wang </a></span>在这一品牌的最后作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112944qCkKATeWHbl09GMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>Alexander Wang 曾为</span> <span>Balenciaga 设计的度假系列</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2012 </span>年 <span>Alexander Wang </span>接替<span> Nicolas\r\nGhesquière </span>出任巴黎世家的创意总监，后者曾担任这一职位长达 <span>15 </span>年（随后加入<span> Louis Vuitton 任女装艺术总监</span>）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t而大仁走后谁来接替，暂时不得而知，但根据一条来自巴黎的消息，开云集团更倾向于考虑寻找比较低调、有潜质的继任者。很可能是受到今年 1 月 Gucci 任命有些默默无闻的 Alessandro Michele 为新创意总监获得业内较高评价的影响。\r\n</p>\n\n"}